  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK884">
<l>maṉamāṇā vuṭpakai tōṉṟi ṉiṉamāṇā </l>
<l>vētam palavun tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The secret enmity of a person whose mind in unreformed will lead to many evils causing disaffection among (one's) relations.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
